Name: Cube Roller
About the game: A casual racing game of rolling a ball through various cube mazes of increasing complexity! Compete for the fastest time to earn your spot on the global leaderboards! Redefining everything humanity thought mazes could be! If you have an underdeveloped sense of spatial awareness, this might not be the game for you!
